claim.claim-text:
1. An automotive driveline assembly, comprising:
a constant velocity joint;
a dust boot seal disposed about the constant velocity joint, the dust boot seal having a unitary body constructed of silicone material capable of withstanding at least 150° C. operating temperature, wherein said silicone material is comprised of amorphous silica, one or more silicone additives, polymethylsiloxane; peroxide and at least one pigment.
